{"id":582757,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/04/【立此存照】济南小太阳幼儿园虐童事件：被噤声/","date":"2018-04-13T11:37:23Z","modified":"2018-04-13T11:55:58Z","title":"【立此存照】济南小太阳幼儿园虐童事件：被噤声的父亲","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>根据山东济南小太阳幼儿园虐童事件受害幼儿父亲自述，他在线下维权大半个月未有任何进展，遂在微博曝光虐童事件，迅速引大量网民关注后，幼儿园和有关部门才与之接触，在多次谈话中劝他走经济赔偿渠道，但同时又疑似雇佣水军攻击他在网络曝光的目的是为了敲诈。</p>\n<p><strong>截至发稿时，受害幼儿父亲微博已被清空，帮助该名父亲扩散消息的微博内容被删，大量网民转发被和谐，相关微博话题页面也已被屏蔽。被允许传播的只剩官方通告和部分主流媒体报道。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>回顾去年曝光的多起幼儿园虐童事件，上述手段显然是应对类似“舆情”的标准操作流程：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Permanent Link to 【立此存照】红黄蓝幼儿园虐童指控：被和谐的与被稳定的\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%ba%a2%e9%bb%84%e8%93%9d%e5%b9%bc%e5%84%bf%e5%9b%ad%e8%99%90%e7%ab%a5%e6%8c%87%e6%8e%a7%ef%bc%9a%e8%a2%ab%e5%92%8c%e8%b0%90%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%8e/\" rel=\"bookmark\">【立此存照】红黄蓝幼儿园虐童指控：被和谐的与被稳定的 </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e8%bf%9e%e9%94%81%e5%b9%bc%e5%84%bf%e5%9b%ad%e8%99%90%e7%ab%a5%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6%e7%9b%b8%e5%85%b3%e6%8a%a5%e9%81%93%e9%81%ad/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">【立此存照】北京连锁幼儿园虐童事件相关报道遭和谐</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"【立此存照】携程亲子园虐童事件禁令图片遭全面封杀\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e6%90%ba%e7%a8%8b%e4%ba%b2%e5%ad%90%e5%9b%ad%e8%99%90%e7%ab%a5%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6%e7%a6%81%e4%bb%a4%e5%9b%be%e7%89%87%e9%81%ad%e5%85%a8%e9%9d%a2/\">【立此存照】携程亲子园虐童事件禁令图片遭全面封杀</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"【CDTV】被删视频：河北沧州红黄蓝幼儿园被曝针扎幼童\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e3%80%90%e8%a2%ab%e5%88%a0%e8%a7%86%e9%a2%91%e3%80%91%e6%b2%b3%e5%8c%97%e6%b2%a7%e5%b7%9e%e7%ba%a2%e9%bb%84%e8%93%9d%e5%b9%bc%e5%84%bf%e5%9b%ad%e8%a2%ab%e6%9b%9d%e9%92%88%e6%89%8e%e5%b9%bc%e7%ab%a5/\">【CDTV】被删视频：河北沧州红黄蓝幼儿园被曝针扎幼童</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n<strong>以下为中国数字时代编辑搜集整理的部分被删微博内容：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>关专题：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e7%ba%a2%e9%bb%84%e8%93%9d%e5%b9%bc%e5%84%bf%e5%9b%ad/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">红黄蓝幼儿园虐童事件</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e6%90%ba%e7%a8%8b%e5%b9%bc%e6%89%98%e8%99%90%e7%ab%a5%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">携程幼托虐童事件</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_582758\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-582758\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你.jpg 1582w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你-300x182.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你-768x466.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你-1024x621.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong><span style=\"color: #808080;\">受伤幼儿父亲微博被清空；微博页面截图</span></strong></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_582770\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-582770\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"405\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你2.jpg 1388w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你2-300x221.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你2-768x565.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/腾腾爸妈保护你2-1024x754.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong><span style=\"color: #808080;\">受害幼儿父亲被删微博截图</span></strong></p></div>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9ag471j319x1syqiy.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-582773\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9ag471j319x1syqiy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9ag471j319x1syqiy.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9ag471j319x1syqiy-212x300.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9a9a6lj319x1sygyr.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-582772\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9a9a6lj319x1sygyr.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9a9a6lj319x1sygyr.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9a9a6lj319x1sygyr-212x300.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9a4cwvj319x1sytl2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-582771\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9a4cwvj319x1sytl2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9a4cwvj319x1sytl2.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/00772tcPly1fq7y9a4cwvj319x1sytl2-212x300.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>近日，自称为济南某电台主持人的微博用户 @璐爷嫁到 贴出了与受害幼儿父亲的对话，<strong>其中该名父亲对有关部门相互推诿、问题始终无法解决的现状既愤怒又绝望。</strong>摘录部分父亲言论如下：</p>\n<blockquote><p>我接触的所有人都在诱导我说走经济赔偿，走经济赔偿的话就是勒索，不走经济赔偿的话就是不按法律程序办事<br />\n什么理论<br />\n他们就没有赔偿的想法吧，就是诱导我要求，然后扣个敲诈的帽子呗</p>\n<p><strong>走法律程序和舆论诉求冲突吗？？？</strong><br />\n你们能体会到我实名举报没人理的心情吗？</p>\n<p><strong>政府会站在我这边？？一个月前我这么认为，现在我绝对不信</strong><br />\n警方介入了19天了<br />\n如果没有昨天的舆论，我去派出所还是白跑<br />\n为啥昨天分局领导找我谈话，都怕担责任呗<br />\n今天教育局又来了，没有舆论他们能来吗</p>\n<p>从头到尾每一个环节的人都劝我们走经济赔偿方式，多为孩子后期治疗考虑，到现在你们又雇佣水军说我敲诈，还能再无耻点不，今天来的几位相关领导，你们看到了不，还劝我走经济赔偿不？</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>@璐爷嫁到被删微博截图：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_582776\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/ea799b7ely1fqb1d49z4nj20u01hc7ky.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-582776\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/ea799b7ely1fqb1d49z4nj20u01hc7ky.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/ea799b7ely1fqb1d49z4nj20u01hc7ky.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/ea799b7ely1fqb1d49z4nj20u01hc7ky-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/ea799b7ely1fqb1d49z4nj20u01hc7ky-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/ea799b7ely1fqb1d49z4nj20u01hc7ky-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博图片</span></strong></p></div>\n<p>@璐爷嫁到 收到的微博被删通知：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/c4fd3afaly1fqb176tod5j20ku11276x.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-582769\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/c4fd3afaly1fqb176tod5j20ku11276x.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/c4fd3afaly1fqb176tod5j20ku11276x.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/c4fd3afaly1fqb176tod5j20ku11276x-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/c4fd3afaly1fqb176tod5j20ku11276x-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下为被删聊天记录图片：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u76gi1j20ku112q6r.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582761\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u76gi1j20ku112q6r.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"783\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u76gi1j20ku112q6r.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u76gi1j20ku112q6r-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u7p46ij20ku112tc1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582760\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u7p46ij20ku112tc1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"783\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u7p46ij20ku112tc1.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u7p46ij20ku112tc1-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u88ejgj20ku112go6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582762\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u88ejgj20ku112go6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"783\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u88ejgj20ku112go6.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u88ejgj20ku112go6-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u94h6aj20ku112dix.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582763\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u94h6aj20ku112dix.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"783\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u94h6aj20ku112dix.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0u94h6aj20ku112dix-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0tm99xpj20ku11240p.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582759\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0tm99xpj20ku11240p.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"783\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0tm99xpj20ku11240p.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0tm99xpj20ku11240p-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0ua8gmpj20ku11241o.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582764\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0ua8gmpj20ku11241o.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"783\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0ua8gmpj20ku11241o.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0ua8gmpj20ku11241o-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0uanj5sj20ku11277p.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582765\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0uanj5sj20ku11277p.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"783\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0uanj5sj20ku11277p.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0uanj5sj20ku11277p-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0ub1yijj20ku1120u6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582766\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0ub1yijj20ku1120u6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"783\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0ub1yijj20ku1120u6.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0ub1yijj20ku1120u6-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0uc166fj20lk4q6dxn.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582767\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0uc166fj20lk4q6dxn.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"3474\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0uc166fj20lk4q6dxn.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/a199df7bly1fqb0uc166fj20lk4q6dxn-38x300.jpg 38w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>新浪微博上的 #济南小太阳幼儿园老师虐童# 话题页面已遭屏蔽：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_582777\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/济南小太阳幼儿园虐童话题.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-582777\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/济南小太阳幼儿园虐童话题.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"712\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/济南小太阳幼儿园虐童话题.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/济南小太阳幼儿园虐童话题-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博图片</span></strong></p></div>\n<p>@璐爷嫁到 贴出的聊天记录被删后，不少网民将保存的图片重新发布，<strong>也遭到删除：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_582768\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/006xNmO2gy1fqb6izjr7oj30yd0l3n0i.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-582768\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/006xNmO2gy1fqb6izjr7oj30yd0l3n0i.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"245\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/006xNmO2gy1fqb6izjr7oj30yd0l3n0i.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/006xNmO2gy1fqb6izjr7oj30yd0l3n0i-300x184.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/006xNmO2gy1fqb6izjr7oj30yd0l3n0i-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博图片</span></strong></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[33561,33566,33504,34334,33559,33530]}